    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a dependable choice for any driver. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts cleanly, providing a comfortable and reliable driving experience. While the interior is clean and the exterior looks great overall, you may find some minor signs of normal wear and tear consistent with its age. It\u2019s a solid, road-ready car that shouldn't require any immediate major repairs.",
