    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical pre-owned market. This specimen exhibits a pristine exterior finish and an interior cabin preserved in showroom state. Mechanically, the vehicle operates with the precision of a new machine, having undergone rigorous inspections to ensure it meets our most exacting criteria for excellence. For the discerning buyer seeking an uncompromising driving experience, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class.",
